      Method to construct appointment
      Parameters:
      appointmentID - ID of the appointment generated automatically
      patientID - ID of the patients (users)
      doctorID - ID of the doctor
      healthDeptName - Department of the doctor
      healthDescription - short description about health status of user
      sessionStartDate - date of the appointment
      sessionStartTime - start time of the appointment
      sessionEndTime - end time of the appointment
